        "description": "<p>BP Messages Tool is a plugin for BuddyPress or the BuddyBoss Platform.<\/p>\n<p>By default, nobody can read a BuddyPress private message unless it was sent or received by the current logged-in member.<\/p>\n<p>Occasionally, there is a need to respond to member complaints about another member harassing them via abusive messages.<\/p>\n<p>This tool allows site administrators to review the messages of any member. They can also delete Message Threads.<\/p>\n<p>NOTE: There is no UNDO for delete operations.<\/p>\n<p>It provides a wp-admin screen available via Tools &gt; BP Messages.<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload and Activate<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='can%20messages%20be%20restored%20after%20they%20are%20deleted%3F'>\nCan messages be restored after they are deleted?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>NO !<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>2.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>improves multisite support  by removing {$wpdb-&gt;prefix} from bpmt_get_user_data<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>fix sumbmenu page bug for WP 5.3<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>add support for bulk deletion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix re pagination<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add default display of last 10 messages<\/li>\n<li>Added language file<\/li>\n<li>Tested with WP 5.1.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested with WP 4.7 and BP 2.7.2<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Allows selection of messages from Inbox or Sent box instead of only showing Inbox.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Changes to readme.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bp-messages-tool\/assets\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1306312\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bp-messages-tool\/assets\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1306312\" alt=\"Tool Screen\"><\/a><p>Tool Screen<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin - BUT really wish is would work with Better Messages Plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/epgb101\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/66bd41fc528db3a5290254580f0d7c9f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/66bd41fc528db3a5290254580f0d7c9f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/epgb101\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">epgb101<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 8, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I love this plugin - REALLY useful - but I had to disable it as it does not work with Better Messages Plugin. Unless I am mistaken I have tried several times - it just appears that the messages in BP Messages Tool stop when I enable Better Messages. <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works perfect!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/alinaalinuta\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/692d4a10a219a53baedb776dad69e629?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/692d4a10a219a53baedb776dad69e629?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/alinaalinuta\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alinaalinuta<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 20, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It is very useful. Many thanks!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great work great developer<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/shawfactor\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/964140058eef83f4d7c2ceb0ac6d2581?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/964140058eef83f4d7c2ceb0ac6d2581?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/shawfactor\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">shawfactor<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 6, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">plugin is simple and does its job, the dev @shanebp is very responsive.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/autori76\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/e4cffb977448c9c8704ef2ba8b88c079?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/e4cffb977448c9c8704ef2ba8b88c079?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/autori76\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Krzysztof <small>(autori76)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 29, 20